<br>
If you write everything in Hiragana, for example, they will naturally assume that you're a foreigner, a child, or feeble-minded.  Hey... all three describe President Bush !<br>
<br>
Sorry... I got distracted there. ;-D<br>
<br>
Also, writing in Katakana is generally reserved for foreign words, or for words that you want to refer to in some way OTHER than their normal meanings.  For example, writing HIROSHIMA in kanji would be the traditional meaning... the city of that name.  But, if you write HIROSHIMA in katakana, it's a bit like writing it in italics... it's referring to what Hiroshima's famous for (in this case, the use of nuclear weapons on civilians).<br>
<br>
So, yeah... while you're learning, you can write any old way you like, and people will take it with a grain of salt.  Just as... well, if you were a child writing English in all-lower-case-letters.<br>
As you become expert, though, remember the opening words to &quot;Wings of Desire&quot;:  &quot;When I was a child, I spake as a child, acted as a child.  Now, I am an adult, and I have put away childish things.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=1185.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=1185.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1185.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=1185.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.threadControl?topicID=1185.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1185.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1185.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><f